data.description: NEW PRICE! NEW ROOF [2023!] And SOLAR power that is already PAID FOR, makes your monthly utilities bill less than 50-dollars for most of the year!!  This house a great deal!! Enjoy this Spacious, beautiful, 4-bedroom home with many upgrades and tons of space for all! NO HOA!! Located on a quiet cul-de-sac street, this residence has had many upgrades including NEW PLUMBING [2023], FULLY PAID FOR- SOLAR Panels [2020] NEW ROOF [2023] Vinyl FENCE [2017], and SOLAR Powered HOT WATER HEATER [2017], Completely New AC [2017] plus a NEW Frigidaire Gallery Stove with BUILT-In Air Fryer [2023]. The kitchen has tons of storage, granite counters, and stainless appliances. EXCEPTIONALLY High 24' ceilings in the living room highlight a bright and airy interior that features neutral colors throughout. NEW INTERIOR PAINT [2023] NEW Carpets [2023] plus Water Softener System, Nest Thermostat, a Reverse Osmosis Water Filtration system, LED lights throughout, and Lutron Porch /Driveway Coach Lights. ENTIRE HOME is wired for CAT-6, increasing productivity for your home office! The 1st floor master bedroom is enormous with ensuite and dual sinks/granite with NEW Soaker Tub. The HUGE Fenced Backyard is incredible. TONS of storage space, NEW Gutters, and NEWer ceiling fans in upstairs bedrooms [2022]. The extra large driveway has ample space for an RV/Boat and extra vehicles. Very convenient to UCF/Full Sail/Orlando Airport and Downtown. If you are looking for a large space with tons of upgrades, and want TINY utility bills, this is it!  CALL TODAY for your private tour!
